<h4>Fluid Images in IE 8</h4>

<p>For fluid images to have a width of 100% width in IE 8, a property of <code>width</code> with a <code>value</code> of <code>auto</code> is required. For example:</p>

<pre>img.left {
	margin-right: 1em;
	<span class="red">width: auto;</span>
}
img.right {
	margin-left: 1em;
	<span class="red">width: auto;</span>
}</pre>

